title: Moto Classic Watch Face
summary: Moto Classic Watch Face for all Android Wear Device
description: Moto classic is watch face for android wear. It is design style of Swiss watches. Watch face feature:- Sync Battery of mobile device- Battery of android wear- Support all wearable in the world Ex: moto 360, huawei watch, Sony Smartwatch, LG Watch and Samsung Gear- Support Round Watch face and Rect Watch face
descriptionHTML:
Moto classic is watch face for android wear. It is design style of Swiss watches.
Watch face feature:
- Sync Battery of mobile device
- Battery of android wear
- Support all wearable in the world Ex: moto 360, huawei watch, Sony Smartwatch, LG Watch and Samsung Gear
- Support Round Watch face and Rect Watch face
